<h1 class="legal-doc__title">PRIVACY POLICY</h1>
<p class="legal-doc__subtitle"><strong>Last updated</strong> July 20, 2026</p>

<h2 id="introduction">1. INTRODUCTION</h2>

<div class="legal-doc__prose">
<p>
  This Privacy Policy for Spencer Frank Consulting ("<strong>Company</strong>," "<strong>we</strong>," "<strong>us</strong>," or "<strong>our</strong>") describes how and why we may access, collect, store, use, and/or share ("process") your personal information when you use our mobile application Dialog Lab, which is currently offered as a pre-release beta version (the "<strong>App</strong>"), and any related services that link to this Privacy Policy (collectively, the "<strong>Services</strong>").
</p>

<p>
  Questions or concerns? Reading this Privacy Policy will help you understand your privacy rights and choices. If you do not agree with our policies and practices, please do not use the Services. If you have questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:spencer@spencerfrank.com">spencer@spencerfrank.com</a>.
</p>

<p>
  Because the Services are currently in beta, our data practices described here may evolve as the App develops. We will update this Privacy Policy to reflect material changes and, where required, notify beta testers directly.
</p>

<p>
  <strong>The Services are offered solely to residents of the United States during the beta period. If you are not located in the United States, you are not permitted to use the Services.</strong>
</p>
</div>

