<p>
  We have not sold or shared personal information with third parties for their own commercial purposes in the preceding twelve months and do not intend to in the future, other than disclosures to service providers as described in Section 6.
</p>
<h3>Right to limit use of sensitive personal information</h3>
<p>
  Some sensitive personal information may appear in conversation content you submit, as described in Section 3. You have the right to request that we limit our use of sensitive personal information to purposes necessary to provide the Services (such as security and fraud prevention), which would exclude use of that information for the AI training purposes described in Section 5. To make this request, contact us at <a href="mailto:spencer@spencerfrank.com">spencer@spencerfrank.com</a> identifying the account or conversation content at issue.
</p>
<h3>How to exercise your rights</h3>
<p>
  To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:spencer@spencerfrank.com">spencer@spencerfrank.com</a>, or submit a data subject access request through the process described in Section 14. We will verify your identity before processing your request. You may designate an authorized agent to submit a request on your behalf, subject to verification. If we decline to act on your request, you may appeal by emailing us; if your appeal is denied, you may contact your state attorney general.
</p>
<h3>California "Shine the Light" law</h3>
<p>
  California Civil Code Section 1798.83 permits California residents to request, once a year and free of charge, information about categories of personal information we disclosed to third parties for direct marketing purposes in the prior calendar year. To make such a request, contact us using the details in Section 14.
</p>

<h2 id="updates">13. DO WE MAKE UPDATES TO THIS NOTICE?</h2>
<p>
  We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by a revised "Last updated" date. If we make material changes, we will notify you by posting a notice or contacting you directly. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.
</p>

